data.description:
Welcome to your future home! Situated in a perfect location just minutes away from Firewheel Mall, Hawaiian Falls, Strike & Reel, shopping centers, golf courses, restaurants and everything your family needs will be minutes away! Located in a quiet neighborhood, you can enjoy football Sundays with your friends and family in the covered bar in the backyard. There is nothing better than relaxing in your own bar watching some football.
The seller replaced flooring and remodeled bathrooms, and half of the garage was converted into a 4th bedroom and the other half as storage. It can easily be turned into the garage again, and the electric door is still there in working condition. Seller is still in the process of cleaning the house, all trash will be gone by closing, seller's kids are in the process of moving out. MOTIVATED SELLER!
